#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.176"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.176:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.176:0.2"
msgid "18. Sañcetaniyavagga"
msgstr "18. Intention"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: āyācamānasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.176:0.3"
msgid "176. Āyācanasutta"
msgstr "176. Aspiration"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.176:1.1"
msgid "“Saddho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu evaṃ sammā āyācamāno āyāceyya:"
msgstr "“Mendicants, a faithful monk would rightly aspire:"

msgctxt "an4.176:1.2"
msgid "‘tādiso homi yādisā sāriputtamoggallānā’ti."
msgstr "‘May I be like Sāriputta and Moggallāna!’"

msgctxt "an4.176:1.3"
msgid ""
"Esā, bhikkhave, tulā etaṃ pamāṇaṃ mama sāvakānaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ, yadidaṃ "
"sāriputtamoggallānā."
msgstr ""
"These are a standard and a measure for my monk disciples, that is, Sāriputta "
"and Moggallāna."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.176:2.1"
msgid "Saddhā, bhikkhave, bhikkhunī evaṃ sammā āyācamānā āyāceyya:"
msgstr "A faithful nun would rightly aspire:"

msgctxt "an4.176:2.2"
msgid "‘tādisā homi yādisā khemā ca bhikkhunī uppalavaṇṇā cā’ti."
msgstr "‘May I be like the nuns Khemā and Uppalavaṇṇā!’"

msgctxt "an4.176:2.3"
msgid ""
"Esā, bhikkhave, tulā etaṃ pamāṇaṃ mama sāvikānaṃ bhikkhunīnaṃ, yadidaṃ khemā "
"ca bhikkhunī uppalavaṇṇā ca."
msgstr ""
"These are a standard and a measure for my nun disciples, that is, the nuns "
"Khemā and Uppalavaṇṇā."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an4.176:3.1"
msgid "Saddho, bhikkhave, upāsako evaṃ sammā āyācamāno āyāceyya:"
msgstr "A faithful layman would rightly aspire:"

msgctxt "an4.176:3.2"
msgid "‘tādiso homi yādiso citto ca gahapati hatthako ca āḷavako’ti."
msgstr "‘May I be like the householder Citta and Hatthaka of Aḷavī!’"

msgctxt "an4.176:3.3"
msgid ""
"Esā, bhikkhave, tulā etaṃ pamāṇaṃ mama sāvakānaṃ upāsakānaṃ, yadidaṃ citto "
"ca gahapati hatthako ca āḷavako."
msgstr ""
"These are a standard and a measure for my male lay disciples, that is, the "
"householder Citta and Hatthaka of Aḷavī."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an4.176:4.1"
msgid "Saddhā, bhikkhave, upāsikā evaṃ sammā āyācamānā āyāceyya:"
msgstr "A faithful laywoman would rightly aspire:"

msgctxt "an4.176:4.2"
msgid ""
"‘tādisā homi yādisā khujjuttarā ca upāsikā veḷukaṇḍakiyā ca nandamātā’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘May I be like the laywomen Khujjuttarā and Veḷukaṇṭakī, Nanda’s mother!’"

msgctxt "an4.176:4.3"
msgid ""
"Esā, bhikkhave, tulā etaṃ pamāṇaṃ mama sāvikānaṃ upāsikānaṃ, yadidaṃ "
"khujjuttarā ca upāsikā veḷukaṇḍakiyā ca nandamātā”ti."
msgstr ""
"These are a standard and a measure for my female lay disciples, that is, the "
"laywomen Khujjuttarā and Veḷukaṇṭakī, Nanda’s mother.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.176:4.4"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ."
msgstr ""
